public class ListBox
extends com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.ListBox

Currently the order in which the attributes are set is important; be sure to set models last so that the name/value adapter and optional attributes are taken into consideration. Note that when using selectedModel(), the models in the listbox should implement equals() or it might not show the correct selected value on a refresh.
